1
00:00:00,420 --> 00:00:02,840
Thanks for bringing me my lunch.

2
00:00:03,710 --> 00:00:05,130
Don't mention it.

3
00:00:05,130 --> 00:00:07,510
You really saved my life.

4
00:00:07,510 --> 00:00:10,050
I tried waking you up forever.

5
00:00:10,890 --> 00:00:15,600
I'm really sorry
for snapping at you this morning.

6
00:00:17,230 --> 00:00:21,650
It's fine. Little brothers are cuter
when they're a handful anyway.

7
00:00:28,570 --> 00:00:29,820
Ka... Kamiki-san.

8
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:34,700
You really need a lot of looking after.

9
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:36,870
Huh?

10
00:00:37,290 --> 00:00:40,290
Clumsy rookies
are actually kind of cute.

11
00:00:48,470 --> 00:00:51,130
Kamiki-san is really handsome.

12
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:53,550
Y-Yeah, he is.

13
00:00:53,550 --> 00:00:55,220
He's really popular at the office, too.

14
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,810
Does he have a thing for you?

15
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:03,520
Not really.
He's like that with everyone.

16
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:07,110
Maybe, but he seems
especially close to you.

17
00:01:07,110 --> 00:01:09,820
Really?

18
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,030
It's probably because I keep messing up
and he's worried about me.

19
00:01:17,830 --> 00:01:19,790
I have to get up early tomorrow,
so I'm going to bed.
